episode: My Kings have an important playoff game tonight.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: My Sacramento Kings are about to be in a big playoff game

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That sounds exciting! Are you nervous about the game?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I'm mostly excited. I think they have a good chance to win

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Are you going to the game or watching with friends?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I'm watching it alone

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Still gonna be intense, I'm sure!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Yeah definitely. I'm already pumped

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: The energy is building up!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I might buy some merch if they win

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's a great way to celebrate!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It's felt like such a long season

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: The wait will be worth it if they win!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I wish I could've gotten tickets to the game

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That would've been amazing!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I can't wait for them to prove their haters wrong

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Love the underdog spirit!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It's gonna feel good to be able to gloat

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: A little bragging rights never hurt!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: The other team is very weakened. It should be an easy win

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Don't jinx it, stay humble!
